data.enText: an insect at the stage when it has just come out of an egg and looks like a short fat worm
an insect in its larval stage

tr: the immature free-living form of most invertebrates and amphibians and fish which at hatching from the egg is fundamentally unlike its parent and must metamorphose

value.def: A larva is an insect at the stage of its life after it has developed from an egg and before it changes into its adult form.

example.ex: The eggs quickly hatch into larvae.
